+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Running .z3 files
=================

Zork 1, 2, and 3 are provided in compiled .z3 format in ${PREFIX}/share.
They can be run with an appropriate interpreter installed from another
package, such as frotz(6)/dfrotz(6)/sfrotz(6) from the "frotz" package,
or gargoyle(6) from the "garglk" package:

    frotz ${PREFIX}/share/zork/zork1.z3
